# WORDS OUTLIVE THEIR REASONS · a message of PHONETIKOS

a message-emergent of the PHN universe — the message · we speak fossils every day. moniker ⟦WORDS OUTLIVE THEIR REASONS:PHN:f69a72⟧

**who —** A blessing said by atheists, a dial turned on a phone with no dial, a star blamed for a disaster — all spoken without a thought.
**what —** WORDS OUTLIVE THEIR REASONS — the universe's keystone message: we speak fossils daily, and reading them is why PHONETIKOS exists.
